Package civitas.celestis.math.complex

Class Complex

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Number
civitas.celestis.math.complex.Complex
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Number>
public class Complex extends Number implements Comparable<Number>
An immutable complex number with a real component r and an imaginary component i.
